<LanguageData>
  <!--Original=repulsion amplifier-->
  <RaceLily_RepulsionAmplifier.label>반발 증폭기</RaceLily_RepulsionAmplifier.label>
  <!--Original=This weapon has an amplifier built within it, strengthening its bolt with much more energy, increasing its damage.-->
  <RaceLily_RepulsionAmplifier.description>일체형 증폭기가 볼트를 더 많은 에너지로 강화하여 피해량이 높습니다.</RaceLily_RepulsionAmplifier.description>
  <!--Original=amplified-->
  <RaceLily_RepulsionAmplifier.traitAdjectives.0>증폭된</RaceLily_RepulsionAmplifier.traitAdjectives.0>
  <!--Original=repulsion overdriver-->
  <RaceLily_RepulsionOverdriver.label>반발 과구동기</RaceLily_RepulsionOverdriver.label>
  <!--Original=This weapon includes a special component that set the weapon into permanent overdrive, infusing its bolt with volatile energy. Drastically increases its damage output but its unstable bolt is much less accurate.-->
  <RaceLily_RepulsionOverdriver.description>영구적인 과구동 상태로 전환하는 특수 부품이 포함되어 있어 볼트에 불안정한 에너지가 주입됩니다. 피해량 비약적으로 높아지지만 볼트가 불안정해져 명중률이 크게 떨어집니다.</RaceLily_RepulsionOverdriver.description>
  <!--Original=overdrived-->
  <RaceLily_RepulsionOverdriver.traitAdjectives.0>과구동된</RaceLily_RepulsionOverdriver.traitAdjectives.0>
  <!--Original=antiーshield-->
  <RaceLily_AntiShield.label>대보호막</RaceLily_AntiShield.label>
  <!--Original=This weapon generates special bolts that matches the frequency commonly used in personal shield belts, allowing the bolt to bypass the shield entirely.-->
  <RaceLily_AntiShield.description>개인용 보호막 벨트에 일반적으로 사용되는 주파수와 일치하는 특수 볼트를 생성하여 볼트가 보호막을 완전히 관통할 수 있습니다.</RaceLily_AntiShield.description>
  <!--Original=antiーshield-->
  <RaceLily_AntiShield.traitAdjectives.0>대보호막</RaceLily_AntiShield.traitAdjectives.0>
  <!--Original=field accelerator-->
  <RaceLily_Accelerator.label>장 가속기</RaceLily_Accelerator.label>
  <!--Original=This weapon has a repulsion field accelerator built into its barrel, accelerating its bolt as it is leaving the weapon&apos;s barrel, dramatically increases effective range of the weapon.-->
  <RaceLily_Accelerator.description>총열에 내장된 반발장 가속기가 볼트가 총열을 떠나는 순간 가속을 더해줘 사거리를 크게 향상합니다.</RaceLily_Accelerator.description>
  <!--Original=accelerated-->
  <RaceLily_Accelerator.traitAdjectives.0>가속된</RaceLily_Accelerator.traitAdjectives.0>
  <!--Original=marksman-->
  <RaceLily_Accelerator.traitAdjectives.1>명사수</RaceLily_Accelerator.traitAdjectives.1>
  <!--Original=splitshot barrel-->
  <RaceLily_Splitshot.label>분할탄 총열</RaceLily_Splitshot.label>
  <!--Original=This weapon is fitted with an experimental barrel that splits bolt into multiple projectiles, resulting weaker but easier shots, slightly reduces the weapon range.-->
  <RaceLily_Splitshot.description>볼트를 여러 개의 투사체로 분할하는 실험적인 총열이 장착되어 있습니다. 약해지지만 더 쉽게 쏠 수 있으며, 사거리가 약간 감소합니다.</RaceLily_Splitshot.description>
  <!--Original=splitshot-->
  <RaceLily_Splitshot.traitAdjectives.0>분할탄</RaceLily_Splitshot.traitAdjectives.0>
  <!--Original=experimental-->
  <RaceLily_Splitshot.traitAdjectives.1>실험적인</RaceLily_Splitshot.traitAdjectives.1>
  <!--Original=multiーcaster-->
  <RaceLily_MultiCaster.label>다중 투사기</RaceLily_MultiCaster.label>
  <!--Original=This weapon contains an experimental chamber that generates bolts almost instantaneously, allowing the weapon to fire in burst with a longer cooldown and reduced damage.-->
  <RaceLily_MultiCaster.description>볼트를 거의 순간적으로 생성하는 실험적인 약실이 내장돼있습니다. 피해량 감소와 재사용 대기시간이 길어지는 대신 사격이 점사가 됩니다.</RaceLily_MultiCaster.description>
  <!--Original=automatic-->
  <RaceLily_MultiCaster.traitAdjectives.0>자동</RaceLily_MultiCaster.traitAdjectives.0>
  <!--Original=experimental-->
